## How to build a screen (workflow for each conversation)
1. Open a new Claude/Cursor conversation
2. Paste `src/design-system/index.js` as the first message
3. Paste the target screen stub file
4. Say: "Build this screen using only imports from @ds"
5. The screen should compile without touching any other file
